premise_source_doc_sentence: Indu Sarkar is an upcoming bollywood movie slated to release in mid 2017 .
It is directed by Madhur Bhandarkar .
It is presented and produced by Bharat Shah .

The movie stars Neil Nitin Mukesh and Kirti Kulhari .
The music is composed by Anu Malik and Bappi Lahiri .

History of Aurangzib is a book in five volumes by Bengali historian Jadunath Sarkar about the Mughal ruler Aurangzeb .
The book is considered to be the magnum opus of Jadunath Sarkar and was written between 1912 and 1924 .
A.L. Srivastava replied to the criticism that Sarkar 's interpretation of the jizya was not fair , arguing that Sarkar had only summed up the agreed judgements of the Muslim jurists .
